      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DANCING DENNIS (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 16.95 beating RAPIDO MYSTIQUE. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings eight times from 13 starts. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. UNCLE DAVE (8) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at this track over 300m behind DANCING DENNIS (17.43) in a Free For All. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Deserves plenty of respect. RUBY'S ROCKET (1) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 17.46 beating Starlight Twix. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and five minor placings to her credit. Leading chance again. RIGATONI MONELLI (4) raced on the pace and got home last start. Sure to run well again.",
